close_reason: Typed automation validation and release-safe candidate verification are merged and proven on master.
body: "## Scope\n\nResearch the current WebSocket validation contract against official documentation, current Home Assistant Core source, and the configured live instance. Add typed trigger, condition, and action validation with local JSON/file checks, keep generic passthrough, repair release-time version assertions, update docs, preserve 100 percent coverage, and prove the scheduled workflow on a clean hosted runner without publishing from the development PR."
